/uploads/2024/11/My-Chemical-Romance.-Credit-Chapman-Baehler-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/My-Chemical-Romance.-Credit-Chapman-Baehler-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/My-Chemical-Romance.-Credit-Chapman-Baehler-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/My-Chemical-Romance.-Credit-Chapman-Baehler-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/My-Chemical-Romance.-Credit-Chapman-Baehler-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/My-Chemical-Romance">My Chemical Romance</a>宣布将进行美国巡演，以庆祝他们定于明年夏天推出的 2006 年专辑“The Black Parade”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/my-chemical-romance-new-song-the-foundations-of-decay-3224859"><b>我的化学罗曼史的《腐烂的基础》是一次激烈、无畏的回归</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>该赛事将于 2025 年 7 月 11 日在西雅图 T-Mobile 公园拉开帷幕。从那里开始，杰拉德·韦和他的同事将在旧金山、洛杉矶、阿灵顿、东卢瑟福、费城、多伦多等城市停留。巡演将于 9 月 13 日在坦帕的雷蒙德·詹姆斯体育场结束。</p><p>每场演出都将由不同的精心挑选的艺术家作为开幕支持。一般门票销售将于当地时间周五（11 月 15 日）上午 10 点开始。查看下面的完整旅游日期列表并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fmy-chemical-romance-tickets%2Fartist%2F859324" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>购买门票。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="我的化学浪漫 - “万岁：”黑色游行北美巡演" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/4xX06JDjJcQ?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><figure id="attachment_3812067" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3812067" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3812067" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/My-Chemical-Romance-2025-US-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="我的化学浪漫 2025 年美国巡演海报。图片来源：新闻界" wid